        "1. **Feature matrix:** Use `pd.get_dummies()` for categoricals (`gender`, `city_tier`, `college_type`, `field`, `parental_education`). Keep numerics (`gpa`, `internships`, `english_score`, `work_experience_months`, `skills_certifications`). Target: `log_salary`.\n",
